title: In-Law Unit / One Bedroom w/ walk in Closet / Bathroom / Entrance
posting_body: ['On Aug 15, I will have an In-Law Unit available for rent in Redwood City.', 'The In-Law unit is located in the heart of Mt. Carmel.', ' The Unit has roughly 650 square feet and is fully equipped with its own entrance, washer and drier, and a walk-in closet.', '  Please note: This unit does not have a kitchenette, and only a mini-refrigerator is available.', ' The unit has a private GYM as well.', ' Fully equipped Smith Machine, Treadmill, Bench Press, and Dumbells.', 'If interested, please contact JJ @', 'show contact info', '- Walking Distance from DownTown Redwood City', '- Walking Distance to the Train Station', '- Walking Distance to Starbucks, Whole Foods, Safeway, ext.']
